:Description: trimmed input for use with Alquimia interface to Amanzi
:             for calcite dissolution

:=========================== chemistry ========================================
CHEMISTRY
  PRIMARY_SPECIES
    H+
    HCO3-
    Ca++
  /
  SECONDARY_SPECIES
    OH-
    CO3--
    CO2(aq)
    CaOH+
    CaHCO3+
    CaCO3(aq)
  /
  MINERALS
    Calcite
  /
  PASSIVE_GAS_SPECIES
    CO2(g)
  /
  MINERAL_KINETICS
    Calcite
      RATE_CONSTANT 1.d-13 mol/cm^2-sec
    /
  /
  DATABASE mpc_alquimia_transport.dat
  LOG_FORMULATION
  ACTIVITY_COEFFICIENTS TIMESTEP
  OUTPUT
    All
    TOTAL
  /
  MAX_RESIDUAL_TOLERANCE 1.d-18
END

:=========================== constraints ======================================
CONSTRAINT initial
  CONCENTRATIONS
    H+     1.d-8      F
    HCO3-  1.d-3      G  CO2(g)
    Ca++   5.d-4      M  Calcite
  /
  MINERALS
    Calcite 1.d-5 2.0d0 cm^2/cm^3
  /
END

CONSTRAINT west
  CONCENTRATIONS
    H+     5.         P
    HCO3-  1.d-3      T 
    Ca++   1.d-6      Z 
  /
END
